==================================================
ANIMATION RULES
==================================================

Tap behavior:
- subtle press-in
- subtle lift
- premium restrained Hero motion

Allowed:
- small scale change
- slight elevation shift
- mild perspective if tasteful

Not allowed:
- bouncy toy-like movement
- exaggerated 3D flips
- loud motion
- gimmicky animation
- app-store-template transitions

Everything should feel premium and controlled.

==================================================
PERFORMANCE RULES
==================================================

The UI must remain smooth.

Required:
- use RepaintBoundary for shelf rows where beneficial
- avoid placement regeneration every build
- cache box images
- only precache nearby images
- keep painting cost controlled

Avoid:
- unbounded image preloading
- expensive shadows on every element without need
- excessive clipping
- unnecessary opacity layers
- layout thrashing
- rebuild-heavy placement logic

Do not sacrifice realism, but do not ignore performance.

